title: 700+ Rocksmith 2014 Customs
description:

Copy the FOLDERs "Customs" "More Customs" "Theme Songs" 

& "Even More Customs" (if you want...?) to inside the "DLC" Folder 

?Rocksmith2014dlc * H * E * R * E * 

*OR just the .psarc files that you'd like...


D3DX9_42.dll is the MAGIC File - Copy To Main RS Folder
*It helps avoid the lock-up when the Song would normally be starting right after tuning...


Google: SmithyAnvil & CustomsForge ->Join->Make your Own Customs/Get New Songs Daily ...


*TRY TO AVOID Having DUPLICATES / OLD Versions...

*(sort by file size to find duplicates if you already have many customs, Some badly named..?)
